Bundle policy
-------------
- Source files committed to THIS repository are AGPL-3.0-or-later.
- Third-party dependencies keep their upstream licences; see
  THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md at release time for the aggregated inventory.
- Enterprise-only modules live in a SEPARATE, private repository
  (panorama-enterprise) under a commercial licence. They are pulled in
  only when producing Enterprise-tier artefacts. The Community edition
  in this repository never depends on them at runtime.

